Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽不見我說的嗎
