Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是被迫待在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是指這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又是？
